snippet: The country’s fragile postelection calm was shaken Thursday, with some coalition members calling for punishing officials from the departing government.
abstract: Georgia’s fragile postelection calm is shaken as triumphant members of the Georgian Dream coalition challenge a dozen regional vote counts in hopes of securing additional parliamentary seats, and others begin to call for punishing officials from departing government.

byline.original: By ELLEN BARRY and OLESYA VARTANYAN

lead_paragraph: The country’s fragile postelection calm was shaken Thursday, with some coalition members calling for punishing officials from the departing government.

headline.seo: After Win, Georgian Dream Coalition Demands 12 Regional Vote Recounts
headline.main: Winning Coalition in Georgia Demands Vote Recounts
headline.print_headline: Winning Coalition in Georgia Demands Vote Recounts
